WEBVTT

00:01:39.599 --> 00:01:40.319
Speak.

00:01:40.799 --> 00:01:42.200
Who is the murderer?

00:01:53.799 --> 00:01:55.120
I am the murderer.

00:01:59.719 --> 00:02:01.439
Do you take me for a fool?

00:02:06.719 --> 00:02:08.680
The yellow powder on Huang Cui's cuff...

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:10.439
I rubbed it on there intentionally.

00:02:10.919 --> 00:02:12.680
I found a Thorn Flower tree in the manor.

00:02:13.000 --> 00:02:14.439
Eating Thorn Flower with fish...

00:02:15.039 --> 00:02:16.560
creates a poison as deadly as arsenic.

00:02:18.479 --> 00:02:19.879
I saw you interrogating Huang Cui.

00:02:20.560 --> 00:02:22.039
I feared she couldn't withstand the torture...

00:02:23.039 --> 00:02:24.639
and would tell you the location of the Thousand Secrets Treasure.

00:02:25.879 --> 00:02:26.719
So that night...

00:02:27.639 --> 00:02:29.000
I saw Si Niang preparing fish cakes.

00:02:30.240 --> 00:02:32.199
I decided to use Thorn Flower to poison Huang Cui.

00:02:33.039 --> 00:02:34.240
To eliminate future trouble.

00:02:35.639 --> 00:02:37.400
You are capable of murder too?

00:02:42.520 --> 00:02:43.360
The Metropolitan Governor...

00:02:44.439 --> 00:02:45.800
wasn't he also killed by me?

00:02:45.919 --> 00:02:46.680
Good.

00:02:47.319 --> 00:02:49.439
Then I'll send you over now...

00:02:49.439 --> 00:02:50.879
to apologize to them.

00:02:51.039 --> 00:02:51.680
Don't!

00:02:52.439 --> 00:02:53.599
Report!

00:02:59.000 --> 00:02:59.879
Someone has arrived from the palace.

00:03:00.280 --> 00:03:01.280
They brought a secret decree.

00:03:01.719 --> 00:03:02.240
Read it.

00:03:03.439 --> 00:03:05.240
Ye Li is summoned for an immediate audience.

00:03:16.199 --> 00:03:17.719
You brat.

00:03:17.879 --> 00:03:19.560
You sure are lucky.

00:03:20.840 --> 00:03:21.759
Send him off.

00:03:22.400 --> 00:03:23.599
What about the others?

00:03:24.080 --> 00:03:25.319
Lock them all up.

00:03:25.919 --> 00:03:26.360
Yes.

00:03:27.479 --> 00:03:28.000
Take them away.

00:03:28.639 --> 00:03:29.080
Yes.

00:03:33.319 --> 00:03:35.400
Ye Li, once you leave, do not come back.

00:03:35.520 --> 00:03:37.120
Protect yourself. Wait for me.

00:03:39.039 --> 00:03:39.599
Let's go.

00:04:03.520 --> 00:04:04.439
Why are you here?

00:04:09.439 --> 00:04:10.759
You took a beating for me.

00:04:10.919 --> 00:04:12.159
I came to see you.

00:04:18.839 --> 00:04:19.519
Don't worry.

00:04:20.319 --> 00:04:22.439
I've already drugged the guards.

00:04:23.079 --> 00:04:23.839
Um...

00:04:25.120 --> 00:04:26.160
Thanks to you this time.

00:04:26.680 --> 00:04:27.959
For helping me send the carrier pigeon out.

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:29.959
You saved our lives.

00:04:30.639 --> 00:04:32.120
You saved my life.

00:04:34.199 --> 00:04:35.279
I help you once.

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:38.319
Consider it returning the favor.

00:04:40.199 --> 00:04:41.439
Let me see your wound.

00:04:42.560 --> 00:04:43.199
No need.

00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:44.439
I...

00:04:45.279 --> 00:04:46.279
I handled it myself.

00:04:49.360 --> 00:04:50.199
What?

00:04:51.000 --> 00:04:51.879
Are you shy?

00:05:06.759 --> 00:05:07.279
Easy now.

00:05:12.680 --> 00:05:14.040
Your wound is on your lower back.

00:05:14.480 --> 00:05:15.680
How can you apply medicine yourself?

00:05:19.360 --> 00:05:19.920
Lie down.

00:05:21.040 --> 00:05:21.959
Lie down.

00:05:23.959 --> 00:05:24.560
Slowly.

00:05:33.319 --> 00:05:34.519
I have a waist guard inside my clothes.

00:05:35.279 --> 00:05:36.360
It didn't hurt the bones or tendons.

00:05:36.720 --> 00:05:37.680
It's just a flesh wound.

00:05:48.319 --> 00:05:48.800
Does it hurt?

00:05:49.759 --> 00:05:50.240
It tickles.

00:05:56.800 --> 00:06:00.199
My former sweetheart was also an officer.

00:06:02.439 --> 00:06:03.439
Just like you.

00:06:04.439 --> 00:06:06.000
He took many beatings from swords and sticks.

00:06:06.800 --> 00:06:07.680
He wasn't afraid of pain.

00:06:08.480 --> 00:06:09.160
He was ticklish.

00:06:12.959 --> 00:06:13.680
You...

00:06:14.800 --> 00:06:16.600
Why are you at the All-Knowing Manor?

00:06:19.120 --> 00:06:20.480
Greed for wealth and glory, of course.

00:06:21.959 --> 00:06:22.720
I don't believe it.

00:06:24.240 --> 00:06:25.560
If you have any difficulties...

00:06:25.680 --> 00:06:26.600
you can tell me.

00:06:27.120 --> 00:06:27.800
I can help you.

00:06:30.480 --> 00:06:32.160
What difficulties would I have?

00:06:34.360 --> 00:06:34.920
Alright.

00:06:38.800 --> 00:06:39.800
Rest well.

00:06:49.199 --> 00:06:50.279
Which government office is he in?

00:06:51.160 --> 00:06:51.839
Tell me.

00:06:52.879 --> 00:06:54.079
I'll go find him for you when I get out.

00:07:00.920 --> 00:07:01.600
He's dead.

00:07:04.519 --> 00:07:05.399
I got him killed.

00:07:28.519 --> 00:07:29.120
Hurry up.

00:07:29.319 --> 00:07:30.879
Take everything in the cave out and burn it.

00:07:31.360 --> 00:07:32.879
Put everything in the boxes on too.

00:07:33.319 --> 00:07:33.920
Yes.

00:07:54.800 --> 00:07:55.759
Eunuch Liu.

00:07:56.199 --> 00:07:56.959
Can you be a bit gentler?

00:08:14.480 --> 00:08:14.959
Move.

00:08:27.120 --> 00:08:27.879
Ye Li.

00:08:28.639 --> 00:08:29.759
Do you know your crime?

00:08:30.600 --> 00:08:31.920
I do not know what crime I have committed.

00:08:32.799 --> 00:08:35.120
I ask the Empress Dowager, Your Highness,

00:08:35.639 --> 00:08:36.919
and Eunuch Li to discern the truth.

00:08:37.840 --> 00:08:39.200
Since you have already recognized us,

00:08:39.840 --> 00:08:41.360
why not guess where you are?

00:08:42.039 --> 00:08:42.799
Your Highness,

00:08:43.360 --> 00:08:44.200
this place is secluded

00:08:44.240 --> 00:08:45.080
and far from the bustling markets.

00:08:45.600 --> 00:08:46.600
However, on the way here,

00:08:46.799 --> 00:08:48.559
I heard the sounds of the Imperial Guard patrolling.

00:08:49.240 --> 00:08:51.159
The courtyard is filled with the scent of orchids.

00:08:51.440 --> 00:08:53.080
Everyone knows the Crown Prince loves orchids.

00:08:53.679 --> 00:08:55.639
Therefore, I boldly venture a guess

00:08:56.399 --> 00:08:58.279
that this is the Crown Prince's private villa.

00:09:02.240 --> 00:09:03.360
Untie him.

00:09:11.840 --> 00:09:12.639
Thank you, Empress Dowager.

00:09:13.519 --> 00:09:14.799
You sent a message by carrier pigeon,

00:09:14.799 --> 00:09:16.000
claiming to have an urgent matter to report.

00:09:16.600 --> 00:09:17.240
What is it?

00:09:18.480 --> 00:09:19.720
What I wish to speak of is precisely

00:09:20.039 --> 00:09:21.960
the truth behind Metropolitan Governor Lord Meng's murder.

00:09:23.039 --> 00:09:25.960
Was it not you who killed the Metropolitan Governor?

00:09:31.480 --> 00:09:32.240
In reply to the Empress Dowager,

00:09:33.039 --> 00:09:34.279
as a legal advocate,

00:09:34.679 --> 00:09:36.240
how could I do something to ruin my own future?

00:09:36.960 --> 00:09:39.399
Moreover, Lord Meng was my superior.

00:09:40.080 --> 00:09:41.919
He always looked after me.

00:09:42.639 --> 00:09:43.759
Why would I want to kill him?

00:09:44.399 --> 00:09:45.559
I beg the Empress Dowager to see the truth.

00:09:48.720 --> 00:09:50.399
You repeatedly asked Lord Meng

00:09:50.720 --> 00:09:52.200
to reinvestigate the old Chaoheng case.

00:09:53.080 --> 00:09:54.480
Lord Meng refused time and again.

00:09:54.679 --> 00:09:56.360
Did you not harbor resentment

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:58.240
and seize the chance to kill him?

00:09:58.759 --> 00:09:59.759
Your Highness, please see clearly.

00:10:00.519 --> 00:10:01.639
Although I wish to overturn the case,

00:10:01.960 --> 00:10:03.440
I know the evidence is insufficient

00:10:03.440 --> 00:10:04.480
and a retrial is difficult.

00:10:05.879 --> 00:10:07.639
But Lord Meng meeting such a fate

00:10:07.960 --> 00:10:09.960
was clearly the work of someone who knew the details,

00:10:09.960 --> 00:10:10.600
who used the situation

00:10:10.960 --> 00:10:11.879
to murder Lord Meng.

00:10:21.639 --> 00:10:22.279
Take him away.

00:10:22.759 --> 00:10:23.320
Yes.

00:10:27.759 --> 00:10:29.519
The evidence of this murder by proxy...

00:10:30.440 --> 00:10:31.279
I have already found it.

00:10:37.799 --> 00:10:39.720
Every transaction of the All-Knowing Manor

00:10:40.000 --> 00:10:41.240
is recorded in these ledgers.

00:10:42.840 --> 00:10:44.320
Crimes punishable by beheading under the law...

00:10:45.159 --> 00:10:46.159
are all listed in here.

00:10:55.919 --> 00:10:56.919
I have one more item

00:10:57.279 --> 00:10:58.799
that, even at the risk of losing my head,

00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:00.159
I must present to the Empress Dowager.

00:11:17.279 --> 00:11:18.320
This is outrageous!

00:11:18.480 --> 00:11:20.480
How dare they forge the Empress Dowager's Edict!